steps.name: I enter skillrary login page
I login to the skillrary
I click on Courses tab and choose Category
I create a new category with RPA
New category should be added to the category list
I delete the newly added category
Newly added category should be removed from the list
I logout of skillrary
I enter skillrary login page
I login to the skillrary
I click on Courses tab and choose Category
I create a new category with MERN Stack
New category should be added to the category list
I delete the newly added category
Newly added category should be removed from the list
I logout of skillrary
I enter skillrary login page
I login to the skillrary
I click on Courses tab and choose Course List
I create a new course
New course should be added to the course list
I delete the newly added course
Newly added course should be removed from the list
I logout of skillrary
I enter skillrary login page
I login to the skillrary
I click on Users
I create new user
New User should be added to the Users list
I delete newly added user
User should be deleted from the Users list
